#### OUTPUT 1 — Images JSON

File path: `src/content/inspo-images/{slug}.json`

```json
{
  "images": [
    {
      "id": "{folderName}-001",
      "url": "/inspo/{folderName}/{filename}",
      "alt": "...",
      "category": "...",
      "isPremium": false,
      "dimensions": {
        "width": 800,
        "height": 800,
        "aspectRatio": "1:1"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

Rules:
- Generate an entry for **every image** in the script output. Do not skip any.
- `id`: folderName + zero-padded index e.g. `lgbtq-001`, `lgbtq-002`
- `url`: `/inspo/{folderName}/{filename}` — use exact filenames from script output
- `alt`: 15–25 words. Unique per image. Descriptive, SEO-rich, nail-focused. Mention nail style, colors, finish, and vibe/occasion. Use the existing blog alt only as a reference to understand the image — never copy it.
- `category`: infer dominant color or style from the filename e.g. `"rainbow"`, `"purple"`, `"french"`, `"chrome"`, `"glitter"`, `"nude"`
- `isPremium`: set `true` for roughly 1 in every 8 images, spread out — not clustered at the start
- `dimensions`: always `{ "width": 800, "height": 800, "aspectRatio": "1:1" }` for every image

