#### OUTPUT 2 — Category Entry

Single object to paste inside the `designs` key of `inspo-categories.json`:

```json
"{slug}": {
  "slug": "{slug}",
  "name": "...",
  "displayName": "...",
  "category": "...",
  "year": 2026,
  "active": true,
  "trending": true,
  "clicks": 0,
  "addedAt": "{today's date YYYY-MM-DD}",
  "description": "...",
  "heroImage": "/inspo/{folderName}-hero.webp",
  "gradientFrom": "...",
  "gradientVia": "...",
  "gradientTo": "...",
  "emojis": ["...", "...", "...", "..."],
  "ctas": ["...", "...", "...", "..."],
  "tldr": {
    "summary": ["...", "...", "...", "..."],
    "keyTakeaways": ["...", "...", "...", "..."]
  },
  "seo": {
    "title": "...",
    "description": "...",
    "keywords": "..."
  },
  "relatedDesigns": ["...", "...", "..."],
  "perfectFor": ["...", "...", "...", "..."],
  "styleGuide": ["...", "...", "..."]
}
```

Rules:
- `slug`: `{folderName}-inspiration-gallery`
- `name` / `displayName`: human-readable, title case, nail-focused e.g. `"LGBTQ+ Pride Nail Inspiration"`
- `category`: one of `"Seasonal"`, `"Occasion"`, `"Shape"`, `"Technique"`, `"Classic"`, `"Style"`
- `description`: 1–2 sentences, gallery-focused, mention key styles and colors
- `gradientFrom/Via/To`: Tailwind color classes matching the topic palette
- `emojis`: 4 relevant emojis
- `ctas`: 4 short action labels, 2–3 words each e.g. `"Rainbow Nails"`, `"Pride Glam"`
- `tldr.summary`: 4 sentences — styles, trending designs, techniques, occasions
- `tldr.keyTakeaways`: 4 short punchy takeaways
- `seo.title`: format `"{Topic} Nails: {N}+ {Descriptor} Designs | Mirellé"` — N = total image count from script
- `seo.description`: 140–155 chars, action-oriented, mention key styles
- `seo.keywords`: 8–12 comma-separated nail-focused keywords
- `relatedDesigns`: 3 slugs from: `almond-nails-2026`, `coffin-ballerina-nails-2026`, `french-tip-nails-2026`, `summer-nails-2026`, `spring-nails-2026`, `ombre-gradient-nails-2026`, `valentine-nails-2026`, `chrome-metallic-winter-nails`, `burgundy-wine-winter-nails`
- `perfectFor`: 4 occasions or contexts
- `styleGuide`: 3 practical nail tips relevant to this topic

